quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  20,114,"Wolemekezeka ndi Mulungu, Mfumu ya choonadi! Ndipo usafulumire kulakatula Korani, chivumbulutso chake chisanathe koma uyenera kunena kuti, “Ambuye ndionjezereni nzeru.”"
  20,115,Ndithudi IfetidachitalonjezondiAdamukalekomaiye adaiwala ndipo sitinapeze chipiriro kwa iye
  20,116,"Pamenepo Ife tidawauza angelo kuti, “Mugwadireni Adamu.” Ndipo onse adamugwadira koma Satana adakana"
  20,117,"Ife tidati, “oh iwe Adamu! Ndithudi uyu ndi mdani wako ndiponso mdani wa mkazi wako. Musalole kuti akutulutseni ku Paradiso ndi kukukhazikani m’mavuto.”"
  20,118,Ndithudi muli ndi lonjezo lathu kuti kumeneko inu simudzamva njala kapena kukhala wamaliseche
  20,119,Ndiponso inu simudzamva ludzu m’menemo kapena kutentha kwa dzuwa
  20,120,"Koma Satana adamunong’oneza nati, “Oh iwe Adamu! Kodi ndingakulangize mtengo wa moyo wosatha ndiponso ufumu wosatha?”"
  20,121,Ndipo onse adadya chipatso cha mumtengo uja kotero udaonekera umaliseche wawo ndipo adayamba kudziveka masamba a m’munda muja. Kotero Adamu adanyoza lamulo la Ambuye wake ndipo adasochera
  20,122,Ndipo Ambuye wake adamusankha iye ndipo adamukhululukira ndi kumutsogolera kunjira yoyenera
  20,123,"Mulungu adati, “Chokani inu m’menemo, nonse awiri, ndipo inu mudzakhala adani a wina ndi mnzake. Pamene ulangizi wanga udzavumbulutsidwa kwa inu, iye amene adzautsatira sadzasochera kapena kuona mavuto.”"
  20,124,"“Koma iye amene safuna kumvera machenjezo anga, ndithudi, adzakhala movutika ndipo tidzamuukitsa ali wakhungu pa tsiku louka kwa akufa.”"
  20,125,"Iye adzati, “Ambuye wanga! Bwanji mwandiukitsa wakhungu, pamene ine ndidali wopenya?”"